Impact & Benefits EchhoPath Impact on Target Audience Enhances mobility and safety for blind and low-vision users. Promotes independence and confidence in daily travel. Improves accessibility to education, work, and social spaces. Wider Benefits Social: Greater inclusion and participation in society. Economic: Reduced reliance on assistance; new opportunities for employment and mobility services. Environmental: Encourages walking and public transit use through safer navigation options.
